00:04:32.510 --> 00:04:34.910
both famous English football players.

00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:37.740
So, why were these two women

00:04:37.930 --> 00:04:39.680
fighting each other in court?

00:04:40.410 --> 00:04:42.620
Well, the story went something like this.

00:04:43.130 --> 00:04:45.080
