00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:46.880
the British press about the private

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.170
life of Coleen Rooney, stories

00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:50.680
that she wanted to remain private

00:04:50.950 --> 00:04:53.500
and not get leaked to the press.

00:04:54.670 --> 00:04:56.696
She thought that one of her

00:04:56.890 --> 00:04:59.080
