00:05:15.530 --> 00:05:17.660
to try to catch Rebekah Vardy out.

00:05:18.620 --> 00:05:20.780
There is a setting on Instagram where

00:05:20.780 --> 00:05:22.830
you can choose to only show your

00:05:23.020 --> 00:05:24.990
Instagram Stories to certain people,

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:27.950
so Coleen Rooney selected to only

00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:30.550
show certain stories to Rebekah Vardy.

00:05:31.160 --> 00:05:34.040
Then if these stories appeared in the

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:36.880
British tabloids, ta-dah, she would know

00:05:37.090 --> 00:05:39.550
that it was Vardy who was responsible

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.470
